OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FEast Kent Hospitals NHS Trust missed
OL,8,Fan earlier opportunity to alert the UK
OL,9,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) of the
OL,10,Fmeningitis outbreak in Kent, it has
OL,11,Fbeen reported.
OL,13,FThe Queen Elizabeth the Queen Mother
OL,14,FHospital in Margate first reported a
OL,15,Fcase to the UKHSA on the afternoon of
OL,16,FFriday 13 March.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
