OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIt's reported the patient had arrived
OL,8,Fin hospital two days earlier on
OL,9,FWednesday evening, but the trust
OL,10,Fwaited until there was a formal
OL,11,Fdiagnosis via a confirmed test before
OL,12,Fraising the alarm.
OL,14,FDr Des Holden, acting chief executive
OL,15,Fof East Kent Hospitals NHS Trust, said
OL,16,Fofficials could have acted sooner.
OL,18,F"We recognise there was an opportunity
OL,19,Fprior to diagnosis to notify UKHSA,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"We cannot go into the detail of
OL,8,Findividual patients' care, but the
OL,9,Ftrust has been in close contact with
OL,10,FUKHSA since Friday 13 March to discuss
OL,11,Fthe management of patients presenting
OL,12,Fwith suspected meningitis."
OL,14,FThe UKHSA told the broadcaster an
OL,15,Fearlier report could have meant the
OL,16,Fagency began its investigation sooner,
OL,17,Fas well as provide antibiotics to
OL,18,Fclose contacts of the patient to
OL,19,Fprevent anyone developing invasive
OL,20,Fmeningitis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
