OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FTwo students have died in the outbreak
OL,8,F` 18-year-old Juliette Kenny, who was
OL,9,Fdescribed by her family as "fit,
OL,10,Fhealthy and strong" before her death,
OL,11,Fand a University of Kent student.
OL,13,FAccording to the UKHSA, the peak of
OL,14,Fthe outbreak ` with the largest number
OL,15,Fof cases reported ` was on 13 March.
OL,17,FAs of 12.30pm on Monday, 20 cases of
OL,18,Fmeningitis had been confirmed, with a
OL,19,Ffurther three under investigation,
OL,20,Fbringing the total to 23.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
