FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThis was down from 29 on Sunday, when
OL,8,F20 cases were confirmed and a further
OL,9,Fnine were under investigation.
OL,11,FOfficials started vaccinating
OL,12,FUniversity of Kent students on
OL,13,FWednesday 18 March.
OL,15,FNHS Kent and Medway said that by 11am
OL,16,Fon 24 March, 13,386 doses of
OL,17,Fantibiotics were given out ` along
OL,18,Fwith 10,627 vaccines.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
