OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774455106
OL,3,CNHS 'missed earlier opportunity' to
OL,4,Craise alarm about Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FAll patients in the Kent outbreak have
OL,8,Frequired hospital admission. Nine were
OL,9,Fadmitted to the intensive care unit,
OL,10,Fwhere four remain.
OL,12,FA UKHSA spokesperson said: "UKHSA has
OL,13,Fwell established processes for dealing
OL,14,Fwith single cases or cases where there
OL,15,Fare small numbers of people affected
OL,16,Fincluding offering antibiotic
OL,17,Fprophylactics to household or family
OL,18,Fmembers or people that have had an
OL,19,Fovernight stay during the incubation
OL,20,Fperiod.
OL,26,@tD@\OU
